                        <interp inst="t18380618-name-398" type="given" value="JAMES"></interp>JAMES CRANN</persName>
                  </hi>. I received money from the prosecutor, and spent it all in the shop, but 1<hi rend="italic">d</hi>.—I paid it to the prisoner.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18380618-name-399" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18380618-name-399" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
