                  </hi>. I received 2<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., and went and spent it in the prose<lb></lb>cutor's shop—I paid it to the prisoner.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18380618-name-400" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18380618-name-400" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18380618-name-400" type="surname" value="BEARD"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18380618-name-400" type="given" value="THOMAS"></interp>THOMAS BEARD</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable F</hi> 104.) I told the prisoner to put the money he had on the table—he took out this money, and laid it on the table—this is the marked money.</p>
               <p>(The prisoner received a good character.)</p>
